components.templateData:
<mat-button-toggle-group
  #group="matButtonToggleGroup"
  [disabled]="disabled"
  (valueChange)="emitResultViewTypeChange($event)"
  *ngIf="resultTypes.length > 1"
>
  <mat-button-toggle
    *ngIf="resultTypes.includes('grid')"
    [checked]="selectedResultType === 'grid'"
    [matTooltip]="
      resultTypeText?.grid
        ? resultTypeText.grid
        : ('resultType.grid' | translate)
    "
    [aria-label]="'resultType.gridAria' | translate"
    value="grid"
  >
    <mat-icon>view_module</mat-icon>
  </mat-button-toggle>
  <mat-button-toggle
    *ngIf="resultTypes.includes('list')"
    [checked]="selectedResultType === 'list'"
    [matTooltip]="
      resultTypeText?.list
        ? resultTypeText.list
        : ('resultType.list' | translate)
    "
    [aria-label]="'resultType.listAria' | translate"
    value="list"
  >
    <mat-icon>view_list</mat-icon>
  </mat-button-toggle>
</mat-button-toggle-group>

SortingSelectComponent
components.templateData:
<mat-form-field
  class="search-result-sort"
  *ngIf="sortingOptions.length > 0"
  [appearance]="formFieldAppearance"
>
  <mat-label>{{
    textLabel ? textLabel : ("sort.label" | translate)
  }}</mat-label>
  <mat-select
    [value]="activeOption"
    [disabled]="disabled"
    (valueChange)="emitSortEvent($event)"
  >
    <mat-option
      *ngFor="let sortingOption of sortingOptions"
      [value]="sortingOption.value"
    >
      {{ sortingOption.viewValue }}
    </mat-option>
  </mat-select>
</mat-form-field>
